	<!-- message -->
	<p>Ok i admit it, i had a relapse and tried to get into a guild on my server to see if i could enjoy EQ again before my billing ended.<br />
<br />
Anyway. I come to find out a truly depressing fact. We arent needed. I mean i knew this already but i guess it didnt really hit home fully till i apped to multiple guild on my server, guilds im in very good standing with and my responses were " im sorry but we just dont need anymore shaman, they would be useless.<br />
<br />
Man does that suck. They want wizzies and bards and BST and basicly DPS machines and healers, pretty much every single class but us. Talk about crushing your hopes.<br />
<br />
<br />
On a lighter note i got to pretend to be a SoE rep to someone that /tell me if i wanna trade accounts lol. Scared them good <img src="images/smilies/biggrin.gif" border="0" alt="" title="big grin" smilieid="4" />  Made me not getting a guild feel a lil better.<br />
<br />
Ahh well, so much for giving EQ another shot. Come on WoW, hurry !! <img src="images/smilies/frown.gif" border="0" alt="" title="frown" smilieid="2" /></p>
	
	
	
