	<!-- message -->
	<p>That's a bit disingenious, to say that shaman aren't wanted or are useless.<br />
<br />
My guild hasn't recruited shaman in over a year. That doesn't mean that any of us are unwanted or unneeded. It means my guild has a large roster of high playtime shaman and we are happy in our current numbers.<br />
<br />
Could we stack better? Sure. Are we useless? Not hardly.</p>
	
	
	
