<tr>
	<td class="alt1" width="175" align="center" valign="top" nowrap="nowrap"><b>Binter</b>
<span class="smallfont">
	<br />
	Disciple<br />
		
	
	<br />
	Joined: Jun 2003<br />
	
</span></td>
	
	<td class="alt1" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>Some guilds on Vazaelle are recruiting shamans.<br />
<br />
The reason for this is because of the mass exodus of shamans on Vazaelle.  High-end guilds are looking for shamans, because most of their own shamans quit or rolled alts.<br />
<br />
Guilds need shamans on raids.  The problem is that they only need two.  That creates a very competitive atmosphere among shamans, competing for those very few openings available to them.</p>
	
	
	
